code: /**  * Access the application context that the server was created in. Sometimes it is  * prudent to check that this matches expectations (like being equal to the current  * context) before acting on the server itself.  * @return the applicationContext that the server was created from  */ @Override public ServletWebServerApplicationContext getApplicationContext() {     return this.applicationContext. }
